Summary: Observed a very large, white, rectangular object.
divs: Sighting DetailsStanding in backyard at 8:22am facing North. Observed a very large, white, rectangular object flying just above the cloud cover traveling East to West. No sound or contrails, unlike any aircraft I've ever seen. Lost track of object due to woods surrounding property obstructing view. Clearly white and rectangular, roughly seven times it's height in length.
